===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|ten}}
Borrowed from {{bor|en|fro|entretenir}}, from {{m|fro|entre||among}} + {{m|fro|tenir||to hold}}, from {{der|en|la|inter}} + {{m|la|teneō||hold, keep}}. For the noun, compare {{cog|fr|entretien}}.

